Bash Subcommand
===============

This is framework for creating subcommand-style commands.

Installation
------------

To install simply clone
git clone https://github.com/fedorenchik/subcommand.git

Usage
-----

* Create the script

    source ~/dir/to/subcommand
    sub1()
    {
        echo "my cool subcommand 1"
    }
    sub2()
    {
        echo "second subcommand"
    }
    subcommand "$@"

Now your script has 2 subcommands: sub1 and sub2.
